  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Have you ever dreamt about being a cat? </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Curling up in the sun for 12-16 hours a day? </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Knocking over mugs just for fun? </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Eating your food like you haven't been fed in years? </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Riding rockets over the neighbours hedges? </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Shooting aliens from the surface of the moon?   </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Then this is the game for you!  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Chaotic Cats is a 2-4 player local multiplayer paw-ty game where players go paw to paw to collect the most fish through 20 unique and chaotic minigames.</p>",
